channel.title: Small Problem
channel.description:
I have had a couple servers and they have worked perfectly fine but something went wrong with my computer so I had to send it back to the company for them to fix it. Nothing changed on the computer i went through it a couple times, but now when i download a source and client i change the setserver in the EGUI.java and in the client.java in the client. But when i try to log on it says error connecting to server. I have checked portfowarding and everything and i have check my enviormental variables like 6 times but i think i know what might be wrong. When you have to fill in the version of JDK you have I cant remember how to tell which version you have. I downloaded the newest one yesterday. So if you could tell me the version that would be helpful. EX. jdk1.6.0_11. Just if you guys call me noob i havent coded in like a year and a half so you sometimes forget things :D
